1. *Optužen* je za krađu (He was *accused* of theft)
2. On je *optužen* za ubistvo (He is *charged* with murder)
3. Advokat brani *optuženog* klijenta (The lawyer is defending the *accused* client)
4. Nije bilo dovoljno dokaza da bi ga *optužili* (There wasn't enough evidence to *charge* him)
5. Sud je odbacio *optužnicu* zbog nedostatka dokaza (The court dismissed the *indictment* due to lack of evidence)
6. *Optužnica* protiv njega nije bila potkrepljena dokazima (The *indictment* against him was not supported by evidence)
7. Tužilaštvo je *optužilo* pet osoba za korupciju (The prosecution *charged* five people with corruption)
8. Advokat je zatražio oslobađajuću presudu za *optuženog* (The lawyer requested an acquittal for the *accused*)
9. Osoba koja je *optužena* za zločin ima pravo na pravično suđenje (A person who is *accused* of a crime has the right to a fair trial)
10. Istraga je pokazala da je on *optužen* neosnovano (The investigation showed that he was *falsely accused*).